death of a relative, and family events.

115
00:06:31,802 --> 00:06:34,394
Personal safety.
We could burn the apartment down.

116
00:06:34,395 --> 00:06:36,464
- Ooh! Ooh!
- Or...

117
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,459
