so he doesn't miss his kid's big debut.

140
00:07:47,146 --> 00:07:50,350
Okay, I'll bite.
What's he debuting as?

141
00:07:53,486 --> 00:07:57,581
Yeah, I don't know. But we're gonna
go steal his school and find out.

142
00:08:01,763 --> 00:08:05,408
- A mister Ando Buhari is here.
- I don't have any appointments.

143
00:08:05,409 --> 00:08:09,470
- I know. Do you want--
- Oh, Dr. Jerrod.

144
00:08:09,583 --> 00:08:11,931
Dr. Jerrod, come.

145
00:08:15,262 --> 00:08:17,215
