private school in Boston.

182
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:18,278
- Ja, ja.
- Let him talk!

183
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:23,555
The Melcher method involves
the education of the whole child--

184
00:10:23,658 --> 00:10:25,483
Mind and body.

185
