I want someone to like me.

285
00:16:04,176 --> 00:16:06,438
Does that get easier
when you're a grown-up?

286
00:16:06,439 --> 00:16:08,326
Um... no.

287
00:16:09,023 --> 00:16:10,873
I don't think it does.

288
